=================
AUTO-INSTALL 
=================
curl -o - https://raw.github.com/ycyang/dotvim/master/auto-install.sh | sh

=================
MANUALLY INSTALL
=================
1. Check out from github

git clone git://github.com/vgod/vimrc.git ~/.vim
cd ~/.vim
git submodule update --init

2. Install ~/.vimrc

./install-vimrc.sh
